    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Mira Cindren — Hardby Junior Partner, C&amp;V</h2>\n<p><em>Veshen Cindren's cousin and the C&amp;V Hardby junior partner who handles official delegations. Polite, prepared, gives nothing useful. The face the party meets if they show up under the Official Delegation banner.</em></p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p>Non-combatant. Yields rather than fights. Has no personal stake in the conspiracy beyond family standing in the firm; will not commit physical violence on its behalf.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 1, PB +2)</h3>\n<p>AC 12 · HP 33 (6d8+6) · Speed 30 ft. · Init +1 · Passive Perception 11</p>\n<p>STR 10 · DEX 12 · CON 14 · INT 16 · WIS 13 · CHA 15. Saves: INT +5. Skills: Deception +3, History +5, Insight +3, Investigation +5, Persuasion +3.</p>\n<p>Languages: Common, Old Aerdi, Suloise, Hardby trade cipher.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 3.</em> See <em>Cindren &amp; Vhal Hardby Branch → Path 3 — The Subpoena (Official Delegation)</em>.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
